017-05-15T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>bg85穿果陣好易𠝹花線，建議轉番80啦<br />\n利申：做緊呢行</blockquote><br />\n估唔到連登有人做羽毛球穿線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想入行 有冇咩窿路 間間羽毛球店都唔洗請人咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accd7c70b69fe153b65b69bd4c8e52a913c41d48","tid":241313,"uid":59042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"有無興趣約下友誼波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a122e2daf9adeb38d671975339173d731645653","tid":241313,"uid":9991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"足唔足磅睇幾樣野<br />\n工具，穿法，手法等等<br />\n最重要係睇精神同心機<br />\n如果由開工穿到收工，尾果幾塊一定會無咁好<br />\n係間舖穿一次係差唔代表間舖唔掂，只係個師傅穿工差<br />\n穿塊足磅既出黎都唔係咁簡單<br />\n有d舖頭會穿高幾磅黎預走磅，但穿uu黎唔好打<br />\n<br />\n利申：做左幾年羽毛球舖"},{"pid":"2e6f53610bab268682182eb9b75cc1d7534dfaea","tid":241313,"uid":104179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"龍黱先易斷<br />\n豐盈就穿過不下10次，全足磅+ok好打"},{"pid":"fa1761d253ba643e55c38ca9e1b84dac9d393742","tid":241313,"uid":29131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍黱先易斷<br />\n豐盈就穿過不下10次，全足磅+ok好打</blockquote><br />\n之前聽人講俾龍騰穿線整花支拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3391008b56151b2b24bd0cdefe19b6ff50a7c0","tid":241313,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"BG85 易斷<br />\n重要講技術<br />\n用BG65"},{"pid":"09ecee9af293c935dfb85beb4b7015fc768dc4a7","tid":241313,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"豐盈都黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個已經係佢到穿都無事喎"},{"pid":"050d8bdd2138a5c666644f472466cf587dc85fab","tid":241313,"uid":29131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豐盈都黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個已經係佢到穿都無事喎</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係個後生個個肥仔問題<br />\n穿緊線都掛住撳手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次買野俾錢叫我等等先 跟住我企係到望住佢覆人wts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905b7beba1a7c5d395882e4e78eafc913699ddd9","tid":241313,"uid":50441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>bg85穿果陣好易𠝹花線，建議轉番80啦<br />\n利申：做緊呢行</blockquote><br />\n估唔到連登有人做羽毛球穿線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想入行 有冇咩窿路 間間羽毛球店都唔洗請人咁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難先入到行，多數係要人介紹"},{"pid":"4f4f1d2b328f57e5aad492c7ac0d19b4b5b45d12","tid":241313,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豐盈都黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個已經係佢到穿都無事喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近穿過一次<br />\n<br />\nBg65 25磅<br />\n<br />\n塊拍 穿線機夾位 有2個位 甩左色...<br />\n<br />\n好唔靚仔到唔想用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n綠黑色既拍 多左2, 3點銀色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879ec4eba46cd653a3ce1ecb523ee50cf313eb1a","tid":241313,"uid":75578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無興趣約下友誼波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩級先？<br />\n<br />\n高登連登...約親 <br />\n<br />\n一係超高手<br />\n比賽級<br />\n<br />\n一係就拍都唔識握"},{"pid":"377bfe74c476bc8cb6d231a008ad191b4b43caf0","tid":241313,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>豐盈都黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細細個已經係佢到穿都無事喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近穿過一次<b